{
  "$comment": "aeloop 自己的 Claude Code hooks（aeloop issue #84：brain 醒来开场白 Phase1）。AELOOP_BRAIN_IDENTITY_DB 未设置、或已设置但身份库是空的时，brain-wake-greeting.mjs 不再安静跳过——会注入一段首次引导脚本，带用户走一遍配置问答（issue #96，docs/first-wake-onboarding/DESIGN.md）；已有真实数据的会话行为不变。配置方式见 docs/conductor-brain-layer/WAKE-GREETING-RUNBOOK.md。诚实标注：这只换了数据源（aeloop 身份 MemoryStore），没有换运行时——仍然依附 Claude Code CLI 自己的 SessionStart 生命周期钩子（DESIGN.md §7.1/§7.2 Phase1/Phase2 边界）。",
  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "matcher": "startup|resume|clear",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node \"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/brain-wake-greeting.mjs\""
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node \"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/brain-isolation-guard.mjs\""
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node \"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/brain-commit-gate.mjs\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Edit|Write",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node \"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/brain-issue-gate.mjs\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node \"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/brain-red-line-guard.mjs\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Edit|Write",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node \"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/brain-red-line-guard.mjs\""
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
